AmeriCorps Logo
AmeriCorps is an independent agency of the United States government that engages more than five million Americans in service through AmeriCorps VISTA, AmeriCorps NCCC, AmeriCorps State and National, AmeriCorps Seniors, the Volunteer Generation Fund, and other national service initiatives. The agency’s mission is “to improve lives, strengthen communities, and foster civic engagement through service and volunteering.” While a government agency, AmeriCorps acts much like a foundation and is the nation’s largest annual grant maker supporting service and volunteering.
You can download theAmeriCorpslogo on full-version of the page.
